    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中国式战队是一款冒险养成类游戏。 玩家将扮演一名电竞俱乐部的创始人，带领团队从网吧战队发展为世界冠军。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/39e71c6e542651180a224411a0dd0e88.avif?t=1727376111\" width=800 height=438 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏剧情丰富，美术一流，角色繁多。在游戏中，玩家会探索中国的不同地区，进行不同的冒险并触发不同的剧情。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/a1b7b386f8a801b80eb60ad7785300de.avif?t=1727376111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras_big/a1b7b386f8a801b80eb60ad7785300de.avif?t=1727376111 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在中国的不同城市，玩家会进行各种大冒险并挑战小游戏。当玩家完成冒险以后，玩家将解锁不同的技能，让战队的成员变得实力更强，在今后的比赛中战胜更强大的对手。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/6a500b7d852e73d07d8674f02d3f42b2.avif?t=1727376111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras_big/6a500b7d852e73d07d8674f02d3f42b2.avif?t=1727376111 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在比赛日期，玩家会逐渐挑战更高级别的赛事和更强大的敌人。玩家要增强各个队员的英雄熟练度，然后渐渐的成长为世界顶级的选手，并夺得世界冠军。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/109abc107562f5f73d688b05313b9805.avif?t=1727376111\" width=800 height=440 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的战斗系统会在游戏中触发，玩家将会使用不同的作战方式来面对很多不同的敌人。有卡牌，格斗和自走棋战斗系统。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/c794a938afa51bfd7137fa5aa0d2405a.avif?t=1727376111\" width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做为一个养成类游戏，经营系统必不可少。 在故事的第二篇章，玩家将会开始获得收入。两个商城系统将会被解锁。玩家需要进行财务计算，在提高队员战斗力的同时，保持战队财务收支平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏剧情很丰富。整个游戏有数十章节的剧情，还有隐藏剧情可以解锁。游戏剧情十分搞笑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在第四篇章，玩家将会代表中国去参加亚洲杯。为国家争光。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/9d6d982dff40536037272a1977c3d37f.avif?t=1727376111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras_big/9d6d982dff40536037272a1977c3d37f.avif?t=1727376111 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在剧情发展中，游戏主角们将会遇到各行各业的知名人士并与其交流。与成功人士交流可以让主角们的各项属性，并帮助战队经营。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/6b821078567a2224c896789aeece6b29.avif?t=1727376111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras_big/6b821078567a2224c896789aeece6b29.avif?t=1727376111 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在数年的努力和成长之后，最终团员们将会征服一个又一个的赛事，并成长为世界顶尖电竞手。让我们一起努力，成为世界冠军。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras/e4bcfb797bab71d694830f58a3bae926.avif?t=1727376111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243960/extras_big/e4bcfb797bab71d694830f58a3bae926.avif?t=1727376111 width=800 height=532 /></span></p>",
